STEP 4 в†’ Physics Validation
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Cross-sensor consistency rules
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Rule A:
в”‚   High current + low RPM
в”‚   = locked rotor
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Rule B:
в”‚   High vibration only
в”‚   = possible sensor noise
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Rule C:
в”‚   High temperature
в”‚   = cooling failure
в”‚
в”њв”Ђв”Ђ Rule D:
в”‚   Overspeed + normal current
в”‚   = tachometer artifact
в”‚
в””в”Ђв”Ђ Output:
    Confidence multiplier

